Nicole Garcia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicole_Garcia 0 Stephanie Nicole Garcia-Colace (born November 21, 1983) is an American professional wrestler signed to WWE under the ring name Nikki Bella , where she performs on the Raw brand. In June 2007, Bella signed with World Wrestling Entertainment (WWE), and was assigned to developmental territory Florida Championship Wrestling (FCW) alongside her twin sister Brie Bella, forming the duo The Bella Twins. She made her debut on SmackDown in November 2008. Bella is a two-time WWE Divas Champion. Bella ranked No. 1 in Pro Wrestling Illustrated's Female 50 in November 2015, and was named Diva of the Year by Rolling Stone in December 2015. She also won the award for Choice Female Athlete alongside her sister at the Teen Choice Awards in 2016.
